{"tid":2074554,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉跳閘掌摑港鐵職員 8 巴　香淑嫻裁定38 歲男罪成判囚兩周","createTime":"2020-06-22T07:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T09:57:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4380ad8f98c70912844d057b0d5c649524f900cb","tid":2074554,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:44:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E8%B7%B3%E9%96%98%E6%8E%8C%E6%91%91%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1-8-%E5%B7%B4-38-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%91%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E9%2596%2598%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%2591%2591%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1-8-%25E5%25B7%25B4-38-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2591%25A8%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=ee878c8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E9%2596%2598%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%2591%2591%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1-8-%25E5%25B7%25B4-38-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2591%25A8%2F&h=3896f118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E8%B7%B3%E9%96%98%E6%8E%8C%E6%91%91%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1-8-%E5%B7%B4-38-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%91%A8/</a><br />\n<br />\n38 歲無業男於去年 10 月 14 日乘港鐵到中環欲參與集會，在中環港鐵站跳閘時遭港鐵職員阻止，其間被指連續掌摑職員 8 巴。他早前經審訊後遭裁定一項普通襲擊罪罪成，還押至今日（22 日）判刑。裁判官香淑嫻引述案例指，公職人員正當執行職務時應受到保障，故須判阻嚇性刑罰，考慮被告無案底、事主沒有受傷等因素後，最終判囚兩周。由於被告已遭還押兩周，預計最快可於今日獲釋。"},{"pid":"e339c624f5f9d0fe71ee4e35655ed61b4a6934ef","tid":2074554,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"永不忘記手足苦難<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef591406a888934ab5f5bb02a07dea8b440f282","tid":2074554,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"8巴吹咁大?"},{"pid":"3a8dce020e315e68681e9ee1a2a2c63f0103eeac","tid":2074554,"uid":271497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"吓 minion 都算公職人員？"},{"pid":"13e2b59a69187b2b5b44880d0ea8ec8e88b25848","tid":2074554,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"公職人員？？"},{"pid":"cdcc21122179574812bbe111e853de7b15899259","tid":2074554,"uid":5737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:00:23.000Z","msg":"私人企業 都公職？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25002a3b90aaac28ae32ed1072af3ca07344e07f","tid":2074554,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:01:52.000Z","msg":"普通襲擊罪坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c045d8ae03a552eae952de3fe69ade3c72dc308f","tid":2074554,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:02:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">手足</span>:<br />\n11.14灣仔站 27歲女文員認跳閘咬傷警 還柙至下月判刑<br />\n<br />\n報導：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/34SE80r\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F34SE80r&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=13a6c784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/34SE80r</a><br />\n<br />\n去年11.14除時值中大及理大衝突外，亦有人發起港鐵不合作運動，其中一名27歲女文員涉在灣仔地鐵站跳閘時，咬傷一名試圖拘捕她的休班警，被控襲警。案件今日提堂，被告認罪，案件押後至5月5日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官香淑嫻指，案件性質嚴重，被告為逃避拘捕而咬傷警員，如容許事件發生會助長襲警風氣，因此認為判監恰當。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">死藍絲</span>:<br />\n裁判官香淑嫻判刑時指，被告郭毅（31歲）承認的兩項控罪均屬嚴重，尤其管有攻擊性武器一罪，一般會判處監禁式刑罰；但念及「被告並非有意圖，因為受到滋擾而犯案」，而且已感到後悔，重犯機會低，遂判被告緩刑及罰款。"},{"pid":"8bad7ba1139e59c2afc40296c4c774ff653ab994","tid":2074554,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c045d8ae03a552eae952de3fe69ade3c72dc308f","tid":2074554,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:02:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">手足</span>:<br />\n11.14灣仔站 27歲女文員認跳閘咬傷警 還柙至下月判刑<br />\n<br />\n報導：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/34SE80r\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F34SE80r&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=13a6c784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/34SE80r</a><br />\n<br />\n去年11.14除時值中大及理大衝突外，亦有人發起港鐵不合作運動，其中一名27歲女文員涉在灣仔地鐵站跳閘時，咬傷一名試圖拘捕她的休班警，被控襲警。案件今日提堂，被告認罪，案件押後至5月5日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官香淑嫻指，案件性質嚴重，被告為逃避拘捕而咬傷警員，如容許事件發生會助長襲警風氣，因此認為判監恰當。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">死藍絲</span>:<br />\n裁判官香淑嫻判刑時指，被告郭毅（31歲）承認的兩項控罪均屬嚴重，尤其管有攻擊性武器一罪，一般會判處監禁式刑罰；但念及「被告並非有意圖，因為受到滋擾而犯案」，而且已感到後悔，重犯機會低，遂判被告緩刑及罰款。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4156482f8bf91295f0e8ce6530f166b25bffc5e9","tid":2074554,"uid":346003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:09:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香淑嫻</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5e5034ab94eb9b5c5d160090d7f410fae44f4dd1","tid":2074554